decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to utilize the Food Chain combo to generate infinite mana and cast creatures like Misthollow Griffin repeatedly from exile. The deck includes various cards that support the combo such as Eternal Scourge and Endurance to ensure consistency and protection. Additionally, cards like Teferi, Time Raveler and Force of Will help control the game and protect the combo from disruption. The deck aims to assemble the combo quickly and overwhelm the opponent with a stream of powerful creatures.
